<Layout title="Meddy Ben Ayed">

<!-- ─── HERO ─── -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-tag">FREMONT, CA</div>
  <div class="hero-layout">
    <div class="hero-text">
      <h1 class="hero-name">Meddy<br/>Ben Ayed.</h1>
      <p class="hero-desc">
        Founder and engineer building autonomous systems and launching rockets.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-meta">
    <div class="hero-meta-item">
      <div class="hero-meta-dot"></div>
      <span class="hero-meta-text">Caelus Industries · $240K raised · $15M in LOIs</span>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-meta-item">
      <div class="hero-meta-dot"></div>
      <span class="hero-meta-text">English · French · Arabic</span>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-meta-item">
      <div class="hero-meta-dot"></div>
      <span class="hero-meta-text"><a href="mailto:Meddybayed@gmail.com" style="color:inherit;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);">Meddybayed@gmail.com</a></span>
    </div>
  </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-photo-wrap">
      <div class="hero-photo">
        <img src="/photo.jpg" alt="Meddy Ben Ayed"/>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<hr class="section-divider"/>

<!-- ─── EXPERIENCE ─── -->
<section class="section" id="experience">
  <div class="section-label">Experience</div>
  <div class="timeline">

    <div class="timeline-item">
      <div class="timeline-left">
        <div class="timeline-date">Fall 2024<br/>May 2025</div>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-divider"></div>
      <div class="timeline-right">
        <div class="timeline-org">Caelus Industries</div>
        <div class="timeline-role">FOUNDING SYSTEMS ENGINEER</div>
        <div class="timeline-bullets">
          <div class="timeline-bullet">Secured $15M+ in letters of intent and raised $240K in pre-seed funding.</div>
          <div class="timeline-bullet">Designed an ecosystem of autonomous defense solutions for the maritime domain including a hybrid drone capable of transitioning between flight and water for ISR operations.</div>
          <div class="timeline-bullet">Led all technical development of Mukagen — a multi-sensor counter-UAS system integrating 24GHz FMCW radar DSP, EO tracking (YOLOv8n, 98.2% mAP50), Extended Kalman Filter sensor fusion, and VLM threat classification (Florence-2) on a 5-process ZMQ pipeline deployed on NVIDIA Jetson Orin NX.</div>
          <div class="timeline-bullet">Pitched Caelus to Tim Draper and defense/aerospace investors at the DraperU Entrepreneurship Residency in San Mateo.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="timeline-item">
      <div class="timeline-left">
        <div class="timeline-date">June 2024<br/>Feb 2025</div>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-divider"></div>
      <div class="timeline-right">
        <div class="timeline-org">Horizon Avionics</div>
        <div class="timeline-role">FOUNDER & CEO</div>
        <div class="timeline-bullets">
          <div class="timeline-bullet">Founded startup designing and selling flight computers for rockets and drones.</div>
          <div class="timeline-bullet">Led a team of 10+ engineers through 500+ hours of R&D; secured 4 corporate partnerships.</div>
          <div class="timeline-bullet">Built the website, grew sales, hosted rocketry events, and supported teams competing in the American Rocketry Challenge.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="timeline-item">
      <div class="timeline-left">
        <div class="timeline-date">June 2025<br/>Aug 2025</div>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-divider"></div>
      <div class="timeline-right">
        <div class="timeline-org">Hayward Flight</div>
        <div class="timeline-role">ENGINEERING INTERN</div>
        <div class="timeline-bullets">
          <div class="timeline-bullet">Assisted with aircraft repair, designed and wired security camera systems, developed the company website, and digitized their waivers and forms.</div>
          <div class="timeline-bullet">Cold called to expand business; gained hands-on experience with aircraft and consumer relations.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="timeline-item">
      <div class="timeline-left">
        <div class="timeline-date">Summer 2025</div>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-divider"></div>
      <div class="timeline-right">
        <div class="timeline-org">Kohi Gum Automation Engineering</div>
        <div class="timeline-role">ENGINEERING INTERN</div>
        <div class="timeline-bullets">
          <div class="timeline-bullet">Designed new production machines to better produce caffeinated energy gum and assisted with automation projects that optimized efficiency ahead of product launch.</div>
          <div class="timeline-bullet">Strengthened CAD, prototyping, and teamwork skills in a manufacturing environment.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="timeline-item">
      <div class="timeline-left">
        <div class="timeline-date">Summers 2023<br/>Feb 2025</div>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-divider"></div>
      <div class="timeline-right">
        <div class="timeline-org">Autoservice AI</div>
        <div class="timeline-role">ENGINEERING INTERN</div>
        <div class="timeline-bullets">
          <div class="timeline-bullet">Designed and tested AI systems for automotive dealerships; tested models and released bug patches.</div>
          <div class="timeline-bullet">Landed 20+ clients, attended a Ford/MOPAR conference, and earned a commendation from the CTO for technical and business impact.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="timeline-item">
      <div class="timeline-left">
        <div class="timeline-date">Summer 2024</div>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-divider"></div>
      <div class="timeline-right">
        <div class="timeline-org">Stanford iGEM Bioengineering</div>
        <div class="timeline-role">RESEARCHER</div>
        <div class="timeline-bullets">
          <div class="timeline-bullet">Conducted CRISPR research under a Stanford mentor, designing a lightweight noninvasive device to monitor blood vessel health.</div>
          <div class="timeline-bullet">Ran experiments and presented findings to judges in a competitive setting.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="timeline-item">
      <div class="timeline-left">
        <div class="timeline-date">Summer 2025</div>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-divider"></div>
      <div class="timeline-right">
        <div class="timeline-org">Cal Poly SLO</div>
        <div class="timeline-role">RESEARCHER · ENGINEERING POSSIBILITIES PROGRAM</div>
        <div class="timeline-bullets">
          <div class="timeline-bullet">Explored engineering disciplines through hands-on labs in a summer residential college program.</div>
          <div class="timeline-bullet">Programmed NVIDIA Jetson Nanos for autonomous vehicle guidance control and used CAD tools to design plastic molds for casting.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<hr class="section-divider"/>

<!-- ─── PROJECTS ─── -->
<section class="section" id="projects">
  <div class="section-label">Projects & Leadership</div>
  <div class="projects-grid">

    <div class="project-card">
      <div class="project-tag">NONPROFIT · STEM EDUCATION</div>
      <div class="project-title">Space Pickles Rocketry NPO</div>
      <p class="project-body">Founded nonprofit that has raised $20K+ to fund rockets and teach STEM topics to low-income communities through partnerships with SEWA International, NASA, and the DoD. Hosted camps teaching 500+ elementary students about physics, CAD, dynamics simulations, and rocketry. Mentored middle school and international teams.</p>
      <div class="project-footer">
        <div class="project-skills">
          <span class="project-skill">Rocketry</span>
          <span class="project-skill">CAD</span>
          <span class="project-skill">STEM Education</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="project-card">
      <div class="project-tag">NASA/DOD PARTNER · CAMP DIRECTOR</div>
      <div class="project-title">AstroCamps</div>
      <p class="project-body">Selected as one of 70 global sites to partner with NASA and the DoD to run AstroCamps rocketry summer camps. Organized logistics, built a curriculum, taught physics fundamentals to elementary students, and helped them design and launch rockets.</p>
      <div class="project-footer">
        <div class="project-skills">
          <span class="project-skill">Curriculum Design</span>
          <span class="project-skill">Rocketry</span>
          <span class="project-skill">Leadership</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="project-card">
      <div class="project-tag">SOCIAL IMPACT · WEB / PRODUCT</div>
      <div class="project-title">Payallio</div>
      <p class="project-body">Created a QR code platform to facilitate in-person, cashless donations for homeless individuals in an increasingly digital society. Built a web portal to manage donations and balances per individual, launched Payalio.com, submitted a provisional patent, and presented to Oakland City Hall.</p>
      <div class="project-footer">
        <div class="project-skills">
          <span class="project-skill">Full-Stack</span>
          <span class="project-skill">Product Design</span>
          <span class="project-skill">Patent</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="project-card">
      <div class="project-tag">HARDWARE · AEROSPACE</div>
      <div class="project-title">UAV Drone Design</div>
      <p class="project-body">Worked with a team to design, budget, and build fixed-wing UAV drones. Ran computational fluid dynamic (CFD) simulations to optimize lift-to-drag ratio and minimize energy consumption across both aerodynamic and electronic systems.</p>
      <div class="project-footer">
        <div class="project-skills">
          <span class="project-skill">CFD</span>
          <span class="project-skill">CAD</span>
          <span class="project-skill">Avionics</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="project-card">
      <div class="project-tag">MECHANICAL · INDEPENDENT</div>
      <div class="project-title">Hybrid Go-Kart</div>
      <p class="project-body">Independently designed and built a hybrid go-kart. Engineered a novel method to combine power from two independent powertrains rotating at different RPMs and merge their output to a single drive axle — solving a real mechanical coupling problem from scratch.</p>
      <div class="project-footer">
        <div class="project-skills">
          <span class="project-skill">Mechanical Design</span>
          <span class="project-skill">Drivetrain</span>
          <span class="project-skill">CAD</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="project-card">
      <div class="project-tag">ATHLETICS · COMMUNITY</div>
      <div class="project-title">SNAP Kids — Special Needs Aquatics</div>
      <p class="project-body">Volunteer swim instructor for kids with disabilities since 2022. Created adaptive activities for a wide range of disabilities, built an inclusive environment, and developed lifelong water safety skills. Varsity swimmer and 3-year letterman advancing to MVAL Championships.</p>
      <div class="project-footer">
        <div class="project-skills">
          <span class="project-skill">Adaptive Teaching</span>
          <span class="project-skill">Varsity Swimming</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<hr class="section-divider"/>

<!-- ─── EDUCATION ─── -->
<section class="section" id="education">
  <div class="section-label">Education</div>
  <div class="edu-grid">

