      <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:baseline;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:8px">
        <div class="edu-school">DraperU Entrepreneurship Residency</div>
        <div class="edu-meta">San Mateo, CA · Summer 2025</div>
      </div>
      <div class="edu-detail">Selected for competitive 5-week residency. Pitched Caelus Industries to Tim Draper and a panel of defense and aerospace investors. Networked with venture capitalists and deep-tech industry leaders.</div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

